"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Cryptocurrency asset management company Mudrex has announced the launch of its new Coin Sets investment vehicle.\\n\\nThe new offering allows investors to diversify their asset portfolio across a wide range of high-performance decentralized finance or DeFi assets, as well as unusable tokens or NFT.\\n\\nThe right financial model encourages risk allocation in what is generally considered a volatile market, allowing investors to bet on the value proposition of the sector as a whole, rather than on individual potential. retail of a single asset. The asset basket is also rebalanced monthly to recalculate risks and opportunities for investors.\\n\\nThis is believed to be the first time a product of this type has hit the retail market, as opposed to mutual funds of similar design and function that only target high net worth customers and institutional investors.\\n\\nLaunched in January 2018, the San Francisco-based organization is going through a moment of expansion, enrolling over 40,000 users and exceeding $15 million in assets under management.\\n\\nIn April 2020, the company launched a digital asset trading platform called Mudrex Invest, which is designed to provide automated expert trading services to ordinary individuals.\\n\\nOn August 10, it was announced that the company had received a $2.5 million seed funding round led by Nexus Venture Partners, with additional participation from the likes of Village Global and Kunal. Shah, among others.\\n\\nIt is expected that the recent acquisition of the fund will contribute to the expansion of the company's operational workforce, in addition to the launch of other products and services.\\n\\nRelated: Portfolio rebalancing through DeFi must be simplified to see adoption\\n\\nCointelegraph spoke with Mudrex co-founder, Edul Patel, who commented on the identified target audience for the new product launch:\\n\\nDemand for a simple investable product like Coinsets is so widespread that we get a lot of interest from demographic groups. The product is especially appealing to crypto newcomers who are quickly overwhelmed with information overload in the asset class.\\n\\n“A very cool feature we have enabled is to allow professional traders/creators and influencers to build their own Coin Set and distribute it to their community to open lock the subject's ability to generate wealth.”\\n\\n[Facebook](https://facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loop.markets%2Fmurex-launches-defi-mutual-fund-model-for-retail-investors%2F)\\n\\n[Telegram](https://telegram.me/share/url?text=&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loop.markets%2Fmurex-launches-defi-mutual-fund-model-for-retail-investors%2F)\\n\\n[Twitter](https://twitter.com/intent/tweet/?text=&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loop.markets%2Fmurex-launches-defi-mutual-fund-model-for-retail-investors%2F)\\n\\n[LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loop.markets%2Fmurex-launches-defi-mutual-fund-model-for-retail-investors%2F)\\n\\n[WhatsApp](https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loop.markets%2Fmurex-launches-defi-mutual-fund-model-for-retail-investors%2F)\\n\\n[Reddit](https://reddit.com/submit/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loop.markets%2Fmurex-launches-defi-mutual-fund-model-for-retail-investors%2F&title=)\\n\\nTotal Ratings: 1 | Average Rating: 5\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/lbyIXVvgAxBfzC2wYXopG.jpeg?height=560&width=840)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1638353185,\"title\":\"Murex launches DeFi mutual fund model for retail investors\"},\"digest\":\"GdJ6EeXZSJkXpSvcbHvzBw7gBguDanpRYCLd3fCV23Y\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xA0be6e535524782c882c8f76448cA356FAc0418F\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"dHzFSEG5FiOdG4uA7W844aIiYKvnpBuR3pA9kFK14pk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"CWWPOo-QkCsYJrk3UhUfd-0H0EUDzOty9BXuHuf0OGo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"qwYV1XEgRyuQQF4hjK_FRJ39U7avB7CCSPn